From 0000000000000000000000000000000000000000 Mon Sep 17 00:00:00 2001
From: Entrpi <entrpi@proton.me>
Date: Wed, 4 Feb 2026 19:40:29 +1100
Subject: [PATCH] iommu/arm-smmu-v3: Add SMMUv3.2 event definitions

Add missing event IDs from the ARM SMMUv3.2 specification:

- EVT_ID_BAD_ATS_TREQ (0x05): C_BAD_ATS_TREQ
- EVT_ID_TRANSL_FORBIDDEN (0x07): F_TRANSL_FORBIDDEN

F_TRANSL_FORBIDDEN is generated when a transaction hits an STE with
Config=0b000 (abort). Previously logged as "UNKNOWN" which provided
no diagnostic value. This event is commonly seen during PCIe device
initialization before IOMMU domains are attached.

The CIX Sky1 SoC uses ARM MMU-700 implementing SMMUv3.2+ features
(BBML2, BTM, E2H, NESTING) and generates these events.
---
 drivers/iommu/arm/arm-smmu-v3/arm-smmu-v3.c | 3 +++
 drivers/iommu/arm/arm-smmu-v3/arm-smmu-v3.h | 2 ++
 2 files changed, 5 insertions(+)

diff --git a/drivers/iommu/arm/arm-smmu-v3/arm-smmu-v3.c b/drivers/iommu/arm/arm-smmu-v3/arm-smmu-v3.c
index 73ac157b481dd..c2d8adc3bc68f 100644
--- a/drivers/iommu/arm/arm-smmu-v3/arm-smmu-v3.c
+++ b/drivers/iommu/arm/arm-smmu-v3/arm-smmu-v3.c
@@ -88,7 +88,9 @@ static const char * const event_str[] = {
 	[EVT_ID_BAD_STREAMID_CONFIG] = "C_BAD_STREAMID",
 	[EVT_ID_STE_FETCH_FAULT] = "F_STE_FETCH",
 	[EVT_ID_BAD_STE_CONFIG] = "C_BAD_STE",
+	[EVT_ID_BAD_ATS_TREQ] = "C_BAD_ATS_TREQ",
 	[EVT_ID_STREAM_DISABLED_FAULT] = "F_STREAM_DISABLED",
+	[EVT_ID_TRANSL_FORBIDDEN] = "F_TRANSL_FORBIDDEN",
 	[EVT_ID_BAD_SUBSTREAMID_CONFIG] = "C_BAD_SUBSTREAMID",
 	[EVT_ID_CD_FETCH_FAULT] = "F_CD_FETCH",
 	[EVT_ID_BAD_CD_CONFIG] = "C_BAD_CD",
@@ -1825,6 +1827,7 @@ static int arm_smmu_handle_event(struct arm_smmu_device *smmu, u64 *evt,
 	switch (event->id) {
 	case EVT_ID_BAD_STE_CONFIG:
 	case EVT_ID_STREAM_DISABLED_FAULT:
+	case EVT_ID_TRANSL_FORBIDDEN:
 	case EVT_ID_BAD_SUBSTREAMID_CONFIG:
 	case EVT_ID_BAD_CD_CONFIG:
 	case EVT_ID_TRANSLATION_FAULT:
diff --git a/drivers/iommu/arm/arm-smmu-v3/arm-smmu-v3.h b/drivers/iommu/arm/arm-smmu-v3/arm-smmu-v3.h
index ae23aacc38402..42bca64aab331 100644
--- a/drivers/iommu/arm/arm-smmu-v3/arm-smmu-v3.h
+++ b/drivers/iommu/arm/arm-smmu-v3/arm-smmu-v3.h
@@ -458,7 +458,9 @@ static inline unsigned int arm_smmu_cdtab_l2_idx(unsigned int ssid)
 #define EVT_ID_BAD_STREAMID_CONFIG	0x02
 #define EVT_ID_STE_FETCH_FAULT		0x03
 #define EVT_ID_BAD_STE_CONFIG		0x04
+#define EVT_ID_BAD_ATS_TREQ		0x05
 #define EVT_ID_STREAM_DISABLED_FAULT	0x06
+#define EVT_ID_TRANSL_FORBIDDEN		0x07
 #define EVT_ID_BAD_SUBSTREAMID_CONFIG	0x08
 #define EVT_ID_CD_FETCH_FAULT		0x09
 #define EVT_ID_BAD_CD_CONFIG		0x0a
